<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Revolve" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Revolve,</orth> to consider deeply, to meditate; absol.: <bibl n="shak. tn 2.5.155" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 5, 155</bibl>. Trans.: <bibl n="shak. luc 127" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 127</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.5.101" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 5, 101</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.123" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 123</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.198" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 3, 198</bibl>. With a clause: <bibl n="shak. cym 3.3.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 3, 14</bibl>. cf. <emph>Deep-revolving.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>